<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>陈梁 - 航空运动领航者</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@400;700&display=swap');
        body { font-family: 'Noto+Sans+SC', sans-serif; background-color: #020617; }
        .gold-glow { text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.6); }
        .hero-gradient { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%); }
        .card-hover:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); transition: all 0.3s ease; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="text-slate-200">

    <nav class="fixed w-full z-50 bg-slate-950/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-slate-800">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-xl font-bold tracking-widest text-white">CHEN LIANG</span>
            <div class="space-x-8 hidden md:flex text-sm font-medium">
                <a href="#about" class="hover:text-yellow-500 transition">从业背景</a>
                <a href="#achievements" class="hover:text-yellow-500 transition text-yellow-500">巅峰成就</a>
                <a href="#roles" class="hover:text-yellow-500 transition">裁判身份</a>
                <a href="#contact" class="hover:text-yellow-500 transition">联系合作</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-4 hero-gradient relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
                <div class="flex-1 space-y-6 text-center md:text-left">
                    <h2 class="text-yellow-500 font-bold tracking-widest uppercase">跨越航模与无人机双时代</h2>
                    <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black text-white leading-tight">陈梁</h1>
                    <p class="text-2xl text-slate-400 font-light">FAI国际裁判 | ASFC国家级教练 | 航空运动顶级专家</p>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center md:justify-start pt-4">
                        <span class="bg-blue-900/30 border border-blue-500/50 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-blue-400 text-sm">30年从业经验</span>
                        <span class="bg-yellow-900/30 border border-yellow-500/50 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-yellow-500 text-sm font-bold">全运会奖牌教练</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1 relative">
                    <div class="w-80 h-80 md:w-[450px] md:h-[450px] bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl border border-slate-700 shadow-2xl flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden">
                        <i class="fas fa-user-tie text-9xl text-slate-700"></i>
                        <div class="absolute bottom-4 right-4 text-xs text-slate-500 italic uppercase">Aviation Expert</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 opacity-10 pointer-events-none">
            <i class="fas fa-paper-plane text-[30rem] -rotate-12"></i>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="achievements" class="py-24 bg-slate-900">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">巅峰竞技成绩</h2>
            <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-yellow-500 mx-auto"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-600/20 to-transparent border border-yellow-500/30 p-10 rounded-3xl card-hover relative">
                <i class="fas fa-medal text-yellow-500 text-4xl mb-6"></i>
                <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4 gold-glow">2025 全运会亚军</h3>
                <p class="text-yellow-100/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    在**第15届全运会**（航空模型项目）中担任**安徽队教练**，率领团队从全国强队中脱颖而出，勇夺**亚军**荣誉，实现省内竞技水平的历史突破。
                </p>
                <div class="mt-6 text-sm font-bold text-yellow-500">NATIONAL GAMES 2025 · SILVER MEDALIST</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600/20 to-transparent border border-blue-500/30 p-10 rounded-3xl card-hover">
                <i class="fas fa-rocket text-blue-400 text-4xl mb-6"></i>
                <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">“飞北”国派裁判</h3>
                <p class="text-blue-100/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    **2023-2025连续三届**担任“飞向北京 飞向太空”全国青少年航空航天模型总决赛**国派裁判**。作为行业规则守护者，权威定格全国顶级青少年赛事水准。
                </p>
                <div class="mt-6 text-sm font-bold text-blue-400">NATIONAL FINAL JUDGE · 2023-2025</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="roles" class="py-24 bg-slate-950">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <h4 class="text-yellow-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">裁判权威</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-4">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><i class="fas fa-check-circle mt-1 text-yellow-500"></i> FAI 国际航空联合会国际裁判</li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><i class="fas fa-check-circle mt-1 text-yellow-500"></i> ASFC 遥控航模委任技术代表 (考官)</li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><i class="fas fa-check-circle mt-1 text-yellow-500"></i> 2025 世界无人机足球锦标赛中方裁判</li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><i class="fas fa-check-circle mt-1 text-yellow-500"></i> 全国无人机足球联赛项目裁判长</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <h4 class="text-blue-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">教育资质</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-4">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap mt-1 text-blue-400"></i> ASFC 国家级教练员</li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap mt-1 text-blue-400"></i> 国家一级社会体育指导员</li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap mt-1 text-blue-400"></i> 安徽省无人机专委会主任</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-6 bg-slate-900/50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800">
                <h4 class="text-white font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">2025年度重磅履历</h4>
                <div class="text-sm text-slate-400 space-y-3">
                    <p>• 全国航模(室内项目)锦标赛国派裁判</p>
                    <p>• 全国青少年航模锦标赛国派裁判</p>
                    <p>• 长三角无人机足球邀请赛总裁判长</p>
                    <p>• 安徽省青少年无人机锦标赛总裁判长</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer id="contact" class="py-12 bg-slate-950 border-t border-slate-900">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">© 2025 陈梁 · 十月航空俱乐部创办人 | 从航模时代到无人机时代 · 行业深耕30年</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
